###
#
# 2.1.8 release
#
###

2015-01-25 09:57  owes

	* updates/2.1.8/ROOTFILES.i486-2.1.8,
	  updates/2.1.8/information.xml: Finish update info.xml

2015-01-25 09:54  owes

	* config/rootfiles/common/ntp, lfs/ntp: Fix ntp rootfile.

2015-01-18 09:03  owes

	* langs/bg_BG/install.po, langs/bg_BG/ipcop.po,
	  langs/list_progress, updates/2.1.8/ROOTFILES.i486-2.1.8,
	  updates/2.1.8/information.xml: Updates from language DB

2015-01-15 12:44  owes

	* lfs/squid, updates/2.1.8/ROOTFILES.i486-2.1.8,
	  updates/2.1.8/information.xml: Update squid to 3.4.11. Unless
	  something critical shows up during final testing, this is the
	  latest commit for v2.1.8

2015-01-13 14:52  owes

	* src/rc.d/rc.updatered, updates/2.1.8/ROOTFILES.i486-2.1.8: No
	  point in having a sub that is used only once.

2015-01-13 14:47  owes

	* lfs/DBI, updates/2.1.8/ROOTFILES.i486-2.1.8,
	  updates/2.1.8/information.xml: Update Perl module DBI to 1.633

2015-01-09 11:54  owes

	* lfs/CnxADSL: Change CnxADSL download location.
	  Newer version exists (-2.8) for newer kernel version 3.8, not
	  interesting for us after 3.4 we will jump to 3.10

2015-01-09 11:04  owes

	* config/rootfiles/common/gawk, lfs/gawk,
	  updates/2.1.8/ROOTFILES.i486-2.1.8,
	  updates/2.1.8/information.xml: Update gawk to 4.1.1. Build
	  without depending on mpfr lib

2015-01-08 22:09  owes

	* lfs/openssl, updates/2.1.8/ROOTFILES.i486-2.1.8,
	  updates/2.1.8/information.xml: Update openssl to 1.0.1k

2015-01-08 10:50  owes

	* make.sh: Directly grab PATCHLEVEL for version checking.

2015-01-08 10:49  owes

	* config/rootfiles/common/bash, lfs/bash,
	  updates/2.1.8/ROOTFILES.i486-2.1.8,
	  updates/2.1.8/information.xml: Update bash to 4.3.33

2015-01-08 08:47  owes

	* config/cfgroot/nic-modules-list,
	  config/etc/modprobe.d/aliases.conf, config/gcc/startfiles,
