	  src/progs/ipcoprestore.c, src/scripts/disk-partition.sh,
	  src/scripts/upgrade.sh: Drop mergeinfo from files in html and src

2015-01-08 08:43  owes

	* src/libs/multilines.pl: Drop unused (attempted) library

2015-01-08 08:24  owes

	* doc/base.cgi, doc/template.cgi: Since it is a template, better
	  call it template.cgi

2015-01-08 08:21  owes

	* doc/base.cgi: Update the sample CGI page. Many things todo, but
	  at least it works correctly now (even if still empty)"

2015-01-08 07:06  owes

	* updates/template/ROOTFILES.i486: Test. Older SVN versions added
	  svn:mergeinfo properties when doing a rename/copy, try to get
	  ride of those as that does not work well with branches.

