2013-11-10 09:35  dotzball

	* config/install/init: Fix "Assembling RAID arrays ... FAIL" on
	  raid installations.
	  
	  mdadm exits with return code 2 if everything is ok but the raid
	  is already loaded.
	  Now we check for return code 0 or 2 for OK/DONE and anything else
	  is FAIL.

