	  "Certificate file move failed" fix.

2013-05-20 17:47  gespinasse

	* make.sh: Clean make.sh by replacing "type cmd" | cut -d" " -f3 by
	  "type -p cmd"
	  Answer is empty when command is not installed.
	  
	  I checked this work even in RHEL3 (bash-2.05)

2013-05-17 08:59  gespinasse

	* lfs/krb5: Fix a few warnings
	  Remove the python hack as there is no more a reason to do that.
	  Python is always build before krb5 and our version is not
	  outdated, even the oldest as possible.

