2013-02-09 17:01  gespinasse

	* make.sh: Fix an error while compiling on Centos-5.9 as non-root.
	  find /usr/lib -name libc.a report
	  find: /usr/lib/audit: Permission denied
	  
	  So change the logic. Instead of looking if find report an error,
	  check if a libc.a has been found.

