2013-02-09 13:37  gespinasse

	* lfs/XML-Simple: Fix download of XML-Simple by upgrading to 2.20
	  Add a comment on the new XML::NamespaceSupport, XML::SAX,
	  XML::SAX::Expat prerequisites.
	  Package look to be able to live without, and unsupported tests
	  are skipped.

2013-02-09 13:29  gespinasse

	* lfs/Net-SSLeay: Upgrade Net-SSLeay from 1.48 to 1.52
	  Add another comment about the libz trickery
	  With openssl and zlib-dynamic, linking here to zlib is unneeded
	  (our case).
	  With openssl using only zlib option, linking to zlib is required.
	  
	  What should really be done is pushing upstream adding
	  -Wl,--as-needed at the proper place.

2013-02-09 08:56  gespinasse

	* lfs/lsof, updates/2.1.0/ROOTFILES.i486-2.1.0,
