	* lfs/coreutils, make.sh, updates/2.1.0/ROOTFILES.i486-2.1.0,
	  updates/2.1.0/information.xml: Upgrade coreutils to 8.19
	  This fix some sort -u issues
	  As su has been removed in coreutils, follow LFS and compile
	  shadow before coreutils to supply another su needed for coreutils
	  tests
	  
