	  is tested, one df test fail and another is skipped
	  Change the tests so they work in this configuration. I could have
	  changed /etc/mtab to a symlink, probably we should in the futur.
	  (The coreutils test that was failing to umount in the 8.0 era
	  with /etc/mtab as a symlink has been removed)
	  
	  Change coreutils tests not to break the build, this mostly only
	  loose time when pure test issue happen.

