	  updates/2.1.0/ROOTFILES.i486-2.1.0,
	  updates/2.1.0/information.xml: Upgrade net-tools to same snapshot
	  from git tree as others distro
	  Snapshot date is mostly the last significant change.
	  
	  Reorder the options to sed following config.in file order and set
	  the new ones.
	  Upstream changed path for ifconfig/route to /bin for some
	  reasons.
	  Restore previous /sbin is simplier for us.
	  
	  Remove saving old binaries under .old name on rebuild, this is
	  useless in our context and produce a dummy rootfile
	  So remove savebin rule.
	  
