2012-05-08 08:38  gespinasse

	* lfs/lsof, updates/2.1.0/ROOTFILES.i486-2.1.0,
	  updates/2.1.0/information.xml: Upgrade lsof to 4.86
	  
	  Add running tests but this is not easy as author want interactive
	  setup for no good reason.
	  
	  Fix our LSOF_VERS LSOF_VSTR settings.
	  This may have been right on some previous versions but actually,
	  this is better if doing nothing.
	  LSOF_VSTR is set from kernel header version and LSOF_VERS is
	  derivated from LSOF_VSTR (dot removed).
	  
	  Pass our CFLAGS using DEBUG variable like FEDORA
	  
	  I tested using CFLAGS += -Wall but that mostly only show unused
	  variables.

