	  translation are not installed)
	  Patch flex-2.5.35 with Fedora patches
	  The hardening patch remove some "ignoring return value of
	  'fwrite'" warning in bc-1.06, iproute2-3.3.0, libnl-3.2.7,
	  libpcap-1.2.1, pcmciautils-018, squidGuard-1.5-beta
	  It doesn't look to change produced binary or to be more exact,
	  does not add more files to the changed files list after full
	  build.
	  
