	* config/kernel/kernel.config.i486, lfs/initramfs: Drop some of the
	  block drivers from kernel/initramfs, they are either not working
	  or have been replaced by better ones.
	  Add ppdev a.k.a. parallel port support, still needed in some
	  cases.

