	  produced code

2012-02-21 23:23  gespinasse

	* make.sh: I had one interesting failure while running a full build
	  with tests.
	  During gettext build, something filed the disk and let /dev/null
	  broken.
	  
	  While trying to recover some disk space with ./make.sh clean,
	  sudo test was broken, so I wasn't able to ./make.sh clean.
	  
	  At least warn that /dev/null is broken as that broke many
	  assumption in make.sh.

