	* lfs/linux: Reduce memory requirement to compress the kernel with
	  lzma from insane 674 MiB to 38 MiB
	  Add --vv to show what lzma requirements are
	  
	  This solve compilation on 512 MiB machines, should work too with
	  256 or 128 MiB (untested)

