	* make.sh: Change use of previous SVN revision in make.sh.
	  PREVIOUSSVNREV now marks the exact SVN number of the previous
	  release, so older version can be retrieved using svn -r
	  <PREVIOUSSVNREV>
	  Auto-add release marker to Changelog, does not handle updates
	  splitted into 2 packages.

