2011-11-10 08:06  gespinasse

	* lfs/Archive-Zip: Add test suite

2011-11-10 07:36  gespinasse

	* config/rootfiles/common/Net-DNS, lfs/Net-DNS,
	  updates/2.0.2/ROOTFILES.i486-2.0.2, updates/2.0.2/setup: Run
	  Net-DNS tests (in verbose mode as result is not so big)
	  
	  Net-DNS-0.66 warn that Net-IP is a prerequisite and one test fail
	  for that reason.
	  Fortunately Net-DNS-0,67 no more ask for Net-IP and claim many
	  bugs are fixed.
	  So upgrade and no error happen in test suite.
	  
	  Change the way RR directory is include, so check_files know the
	  files below RR are include.
	  As I am there, do not include X25.pm as I doubt we would use that
	  part.

