2011-10-14 06:53  gespinasse

	* lfs/glibc: There is a bit of difference in the log if we run
	  tests or not.
	  After tests were run, make install compile format.lds.so and pass
	  CC="i486-linux-gnu-gcc ..." with flags written to configparms to
	  test-installation.pl
	  
	  So we need at end of tests to set again confiarms with the
	  content before the tests.
	  
	  That should change nothing but log diff between build with and
	  without test.
	  By luck, no change result in /usr/lib/libc.so.6

