	  Use the .xz package
	  Run the test when asked so

2011-10-12 20:58  gespinasse

	* make.sh: When I switched to compile pax-utils on toolchain, it
	  look I forgot to remove compilation on stage3.
	  As there is PREFIX=/$(TOOLS_DIR) on compilation, nothing is
	  installed in the path POSTBUILD is looking for.
	  This explain why the missing_rootfile trick did not trigger.

