	* langs/es_ES/install.po, langs/es_ES/ipcop.po,
	  updates/1.9.21/ROOTFILES.i486-1.9.21: Spanish translation fixes.

2011-09-17 09:03  gespinasse

	* lfs/check_files: find PKG_NAME to match the file name
	  
	  Give PKG_NAME prefile to all produced log here
	  
	  Inside find, we don't need to use recursive -R option for
	  scanelf, this speed a bit the search
	  
	  Search for configure WARNING in a separate log, compilation
	  warning file is so big
	  
	  Add a TODO, I have some code to fill that, not yet really checked

2011-09-17 08:02  gespinasse

	* lfs/rrdtool, updates/1.9.21/ROOTFILES.i486-1.9.21,
	  updates/1.9.21/information.xml: Use our compilation timestamp
	  hack for rrdtool
	  Simplify rd_cv_ms_async=ok using that instruction on configure
	  directly
	  
	  Remove deprecated options fixing this warning
	  configure: WARNING: unrecognized options: --disable-libintl,
	  --enable-local-libpng, --enable-local-zlib, --enable-latin2
	  
	  We don't need to disable language we haven't build like lua and
	  ruby, only disabling tcl and python is enought
	  
	  I tested a Fedora hack that remove rpath from RRDs.so.
	  That work but I am unsure this is really needed, so that part
	  stay commented.
	  
	  rrtool is only include in update, so everyone will have the same
	  file with same timestamp

2011-09-16 15:46  gespinasse

	* config/rootfiles/common/cppunit, lfs/cppunit, lfs/squid, make.sh:
	  Add cppunit, nothing include
	  This allow us to run squid make check

