	* lfs/squid, updates/1.9.21/ROOTFILES.i486-1.9.21,
	  updates/1.9.21/information.xml: Upgrade squid to 3.1.15
	  
	  Add a comment for ac_cv_func_tempnam=yes, without that,
	  compilation fail
	  Unclear why we need this, Gentoo don't use that with similar
	  hardening.

