	* src/scripts/disk-partition.sh: Use 1 MiB as starting point for
	  root partition. This leaves a small gap, but should be better for
	  performance etc.. Some disks give trouble because the disk is
	  smaller than advertised, not sure if there is an easy way around
	  that.

