2011-06-28 20:12  eoberlander

	* lfs/linux: grsecurity patch changed from ...251302 to ...251441

2011-06-28 06:29  gespinasse

	* lfs/perl, src/patches/perl-5.10.1-libc-2.patch: Fix libc patch
	  for perl-5.10.1
	  We have to include the patch in our tree, I doubt LFS will fix
	  code that old.
	  
	  Wrong patch produce a bogus -DLIBC="/tools_i486/lib/libc-2.7.so"
	  for Dynaloader (where libc-2.7.so is my host libc)
	  It may no break because we do not use dynamic loaded perl modules
	  on toolchain.
	  
	  We need not to apply libc patch on final perl.
	  That would fail to find libc in ${prefix}/lib/libc.so.6 with
	  --prefix=/usr
	  
	  --Cette ligne, et les suivantes ci-dessous, seront ignores--
	  
	  M lfs/perl
	  A src/patches/perl-5.10.1-libc-2.patch

