	  updates/1.9.20/information.xml: Upgrade grep to 2.8 that include
	  minor fixes
	  For character in 0x80..0xff and in some locales, that no more
	  FAIL on 2.8
	  printf '\xff\n'|grep "$(printf '[\xff]')" || echo FAIL

