	* lfs/xz: Unbreak x86_64 toolchain build
	  We are actually in a linux32 shell, so force to use
	  --build=$(MACHINE) as we are before first gcc is used
	  
	  Unsure this is the right thing to force first a linux32 shell at
	  that time.
	  But for now, this is the only thing tested.

