	* make.sh: Use bash -x for toolchain_make, so we could see in log
	  when WRAPPER_32BIT is used
	  Place install near make as that does not matter where it is vs
	  the env variables
	  we create and it look more clear so, at least for me.
	  
	  Change make.sh to compile pcre before glib, so glib could use
	  system pcre
	  
	  Minor simplification on PASS handling

