	* lfs/CnxADSL: Workaround a code issue that our gcc learn not to
	  accept by default

2010-12-23 07:35  owes

	* src/misc-progs/setfwrules.c: Add --emergency command line option.
	  setfwrules --emergency will (re)enable Admin access for GREEN and
	  remove MAC filter. This gives Admin access for GUI and SSH from
	  GREEN in case Admin has locked himself out.
	  Needs documentation.

2010-12-23 07:06  gespinasse

	* lfs/coreutils, updates/1.9.18/ROOTFILES.i486-1.9.18,
	  updates/1.9.18/information.xml: Upgrade coreutils to 8.8
	  This mostly fix various sort bug (with parallel mainly)

2010-12-22 15:08  owes

