	  need that (build and toolchain)

2010-12-04 12:19  gespinasse

	* make.sh: Remove unneeded NICE=${NICE}

2010-12-04 11:43  gespinasse

	* make.sh: Fix niceness when started as non-root
	  Running ./make.sh shell and nice show 0 when 10 default value was
	  intented
	  
	  Instead to renice make.sh itself, nice the children with sudo
	  nice -n $NICE chroot
	  
	  You will need to reconfigure sudoers
	  make.sh will display the new lines to be include at first run

