2010-11-18 21:24  gespinasse

	* config/rootfiles/common/libxml2, lfs/libxml2,
	  updates/1.9.18/ROOTFILES.i486-1.9.18,
	  updates/1.9.18/information.xml, updates/1.9.18/setup: Upgrade
	  libxml2 to 2.7.8
	  This fix CVE-2010-4008
	  
	  Add libpng update in xml information
	  
