2010-11-12 17:10  gespinasse

	* lfs/update: To much work on expect package, fix the typo in
	  comment

2010-11-12 16:55  gespinasse

	* lfs/expect, make.sh: Upgrade expect to 5.45
	  Following LFS way, test suite result is worst at every release.
	  
	  I tested the way DIY build tcl/expect/dejagnu and experience
	  prove result is better.
	  Instead of being build just after gcc, let it build at the end of
	  our toolchain (chap 5 in LFS).
	  There, test suite is perfect instead of 17 errors with 5.45.

