	  nobody
	  as that produced 250 KB of non important lines

2010-10-17 06:41  gespinasse

	* lfs/gcc: Fix the script that should make gcc -m64 working but not
	  really yet

2010-10-17 06:34  gespinasse

	* lfs/linux: Fix kernel compilation on ppc where the kernel look to
	  use ld directly and not gcc to link.
	  This drive to
	  ld: unrecognized option '-Wl,--hash-style=gnu'
	  So reset LDFLAGS too at start of script
	  
	  Fix the gcc target on sparc to match the link we create but
	  compilation with gcc -m64 still did not yet work.

