2010-10-11 06:13  gespinasse

	* config/rootfiles/arch_i486/gcc, lfs/gcc: Upgrade gcc to 4.4.5
	  Tweak the test suite to have less failure
	  DEJAGNU_TIMEOUT=900 instead of default 300, that look to remove 6
	  g++.dg and 7 gcc.dg/gomp failures
	  Setting ulimit from 8192 to 16384 remove 6
	  gcc.c-torture/compile/limits-exprparen.c failures
	  
	  Double the tests (coverage and time) adding
	  unix/-fstack-protector test target
	  This show 2 new errors that should not matter too much as with
	  -O0
	  
	  Fix a which usage when which is not yet build
	  
	  No patchs yet extracted from debian gcc-4.4 package, maybe later

