	* lfs/openswan, src/patches/openswan-2.6.26-git2010-04-22.patch,
	  src/patches/openswan-2.6.26-git2010-05-14.patch: Upgrade Openswan
	  to 2.6.26rc1 with latest modifications from GIT.

