2010-04-11 10:37  gespinasse

	* config/rootfiles/common/iptables, lfs/iptables: A small detail
	  
	  man pkgconfig say
	  By default, pkg-config looks in the directory
	  prefix/lib/pkgconfig
	  So with prefix=usr, the .pc file has to be in /usr/lib/pkgconfig
	  
	  So define pkgconfigdir like BLFS do, and the .pc file is where it
	  should

2010-04-11 09:40  gespinasse

	* config/rootfiles/common/bison, lfs/bison: Upgrade bison to 2.4.2
	  disable nls as nothing is include in iso
	  
	  Maybe we could disable yacc and liby.a build in configure?
	  I would need to fully rebuild and run all tests to be sure

