	  hurt.

2010-02-19 22:31  gespinasse

	* lfs/initramfs, updates/1.9.13/setup: Since drivers.img is no more
	  used, we miss to include an up to date modules.dep
	  As the result fcdsl drivers are not listed there (with kernelcapi
	  dep)
	  Same problem with pulsar and atm dep
	  
	  So build modules.dep each time we build and refresh modules.dep
	  on already installed machine

2010-02-19 19:02  gespinasse

	* config/rootfiles/common/module-init-tools, updates/1.9.13/setup:
	  Inspired partially by SF #2946071 and my own experience, I think
	  we should remove insmod and rmmod.
	  - insmod does not support compressed modules,
	  - you need to manually load module dependencies manually
	  
	  modprobe -r simply could replace rmmod

2010-02-18 15:30  owes

	* updates/1.9.13/ROOTFILES.i486-1.9.13: Add liblber.so into upgrade

2010-02-18 15:25  owes

	* html/cgi-bin/dhcp.cgi, updates/1.9.13/ROOTFILES.i486-1.9.13:
	  Convert MAC addresses to lower case.
	  Fix sorting fixed leases on IP, the first key field includes the
	  MAC address so it must start at offset 18 to skip the MAC.

2010-02-18 15:22  owes

	* updates/1.9.13/setup: Stop dnsmasq before upgrading to new
	  version.

2010-02-18 14:00  owes

