2010-02-06 20:22  dotzball

	* src/libs/DataAccess.pl: Rename default OpenVPN interface from
	  (one of) 'OpenVPN-Red' or 'OpenVPN-Blue'
	  to 'OpenVPN-RW' as we have only one OpenVPN interface. This
	  interface is used
	  for all OpenVPN roadwarrior connections (red + blue).
	  
	  Orange OpenVPN has been dropped in rev 4034.

