	* src/libs/header.pl, updates/1.9.11/ROOTFILES.i486-1.9.11: After
	  playing around with connection profiles on a DHCP configured
	  IPCop, I noticed that index.cgi tried to find and display
	  connection speed.
	  Fix that.

